<title>USA: RESEARCH ALERT - Cadbury downgraded.</title>
<headline>RESEARCH ALERT - Cadbury downgraded.</headline>
<dateline>NEW YORK 1997-08-18</dateline>
<text>
<p>Oppenheimer confirmed on Monday it had cut its rating on Cadbury Schweppes Plc to market perform from buy, based on valuation.</p>
<p>-- Analyst Roy Burry said the company's turnaround and repositioning, which had been the basis for his recommendation, were visible in the earnings.</p>
<p>-- Also, the shares have outperformed the British stock makret, he said.</p>
<p>-- Cadbury was off 6/16 to 38-15/16 on the New York Stock Exchange.</p>
<p>((--Wall Street Desk))</p>
